bonfyre-speechloop — whisper → transform → piper speech engine

Usage:
  bonfyre-speechloop transform <input-audio> <out-dir>
    [--voice-model PATH] [--model NAME] [--compress] [--brief]

  bonfyre-speechloop narrate-brief <brief-dir> <out-dir>
    [--voice-model PATH]

The transform loop:
  audio → transcribe → clean → [paragraph → brief] → narrate → new audio

The narrate-brief shortcut:
  existing brief.md → narrate → audio recap
